We are heavily (ab)using the enhanced Blazor forms introduced in .NET 8. We do not use any Blazor interactivity all (neither Server nor WASM). Just SSR, Enhanced Forms, Streaming Rendering and some client side interactivity provided by HTMX and AlpineJS. 

